codeText: protected final void process(final Object result) {_        Exchange exchange = getEndpoint().createExchange()__        try {_            exchange.getIn().setBody(result)__            getProcessor().process(exchange)__        } catch (Exception e) {_            if (exchange.getException() != null) {_                getExceptionHandler().handleException("Error processing exchange", exchange, exchange.getException())__            }_        }_    }
